text: Dubrovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Bolshekarkalinksy Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 83 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 22 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 7 km from Bolshiye Karkaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Dubrovka, Miyakinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
